snippet.textDisplay:
iKON has June, that unique raw powerful vocal, a composer with a handsomeness and manly appeal oozing too much; bobby spitting fire in raps and all that swag, also a composer; Dk dancing king that he is with a sweet voice like that of an angel, not to mention a composer as well; Jinan so squishy but dances so sexily, owning a terribly good vocal, Yunyheong world's most handsome chef with the purest heart and the corniest jokes, his vocals could shake the ground though and his falsetto? just listen to him, i can't explain all day, then Chanwoo with a mix of handsome and cute, sweet and savage, clever, sly, maknae on top, smart at best, tech savvy, a slave of the video game world. Not to mention world's greatest songwriter and leader hanbin. Yall not agreeing that he is the best leader, go watch his journey, compare him to others, study this young man and then come back to me. 


In conclusion, there's no other group like iKON--  just the right blend of art, talent, overwork, skills, visuals, vocals, dancers, mischief, insanity. I'm tired. You may continue the list.

snippet.textDisplay:
after i watch this for the first time yeah for the first time even tho im a ikonic i want to share something  i been a fan of ikon since love scenario era the day i watch its teaser i tell to myself im gonna fangirl this group cause their song is my style i watched and waited to all of their performance at first i just like their songs face and charisma but when ikon tv started i just love them even more i discovered who they really are and i supported them even more im so happy to all of their achievements in 2018 song of the year,songwriter of the year, production team of the year it all happened in 2018 i know that since debut to 2017 they really had a hard time and then suddenly they have it all in 2018 i thought in the next year ikon will be more popular and be discovered and they will rule kpop in the next years 


But then.... when BI/hanbin departured to ikon i feel like my world in kpop suddenly stop i feel like its not true bi wouldnt do it but it just happened i felt really sad feeling regretfull and unfair cause ikon is just starting,they  already building their fame and recogtion and suddenly a bad timing just happened again.all of them are my bias as in i cant choose to them but hanbin he plays the biggest role in ikon.After habin left and when they announced that ikon will comeback i felt happyi thought i think it would be okay a little cause leaving members in group is normal but when i watched ikon ot6 perf i cant help but to cry it doesnt feel the same way i want to be positive to the boys and support the comeback but just miss hanbin even more so it turns out i didnt watched their performance again i felt bad cause havent watch an ikon ot6 perf for several months already and i just saw this vid in my recommendation and i thought that i think its fine just to watch again this vid but it still hurts me and i think will forever hurt me as an ikonic. 


i just want to share this story of mine cause this song,this perf makes me so emotional about ikon and i just misses hanbin even more i know YG is an ass and a shitty company for not treating groups well but i i still want hanbin to comeback to the company,comeback to to ikon and just continue their unfinished building which is all of ikons recogntion and fame in 2018 i want to be selfish but hanbin plss comeback to Yg again go back to ikon and be the best leader, songwriter of ikon and kpop again i really hope that ikon will be much stronger again this 2020 I LOVE YOUUU IKON SO MUCHHHHH

snippet.textDisplay:
I haven't been part of this fandom for a long time, i'll have to admit. Even though i have been listening to ikon ever since their debut, i never quite got myself into watching their variety shows, etc.
Now, after finally getting to know all seven of the members, i regret not having done so sooner. My heart breaks a little every time I see them, and even tho i started smiling like an idiot at the beginning of this video, i only lasted until the 2:00 minute mark before bursting into tears.
My heart is heavy with guilt, yet overflowing with thankfulness and adoration for these guys.
I just genuinely hope they receive all the happiness and satisfaction life has to offer.
I'm sorry for getting so emotional.
snippet.textOriginal:
I haven't been part of this fandom for a long time, i'll have to admit. Even though i have been listening to ikon ever since their debut, i never quite got myself into watching their variety shows, etc.
Now, after finally getting to know all seven of the members, i regret not having done so sooner. My heart breaks a little every time I see them, and even tho i started smiling like an idiot at the beginning of this video, i only lasted until the 2:00 minute mark before bursting into tears.
My heart is heavy with guilt, yet overflowing with thankfulness and adoration for these guys.
I just genuinely hope they receive all the happiness and satisfaction life has to offer.
I'm sorry for getting so emotional.
